### What does the dataset represent?

Land ownership types are divided into four categories: Federal, State, Tribal, and Private ownership. This dataset also includes official land use designation, the administrator of the parcel, and the area of the parcel in square meters. For a full explanation of the field names and descriptions, please see the [schema summary](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1CW9Y8MgxBEo53Hzs7ZdKeAfFeG_6cGwN4WOzAIBDreU/edit?usp=sharing).

### How was the dataset created?

